{
  "id": "adv_event_2409_01_05",
  "title": "恐ろしい\nモンスター",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "演出家",
      "speakerNameEn": "Director",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_05-enshutu001.m4a",
      "text": "――そこまで\n…………及第点、ギリギリかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――That's it.\n……Passing grade‚ just barely",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 5.4733334541000005,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_05-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "あ、ありがとうございます！\nそしたらうち、舞台公演には……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "T-Thank you!\nThen I‚ for the stage performance…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.6666667302,
      "endTime": 11.3875284512,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "演出家",
      "speakerNameEn": "Director",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_05-enshutu002.m4a",
      "text": "えぇ、降板はなし。当初の予定通りでいきましょう\n……でも慢心しないで。あなた……下手、なんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ no one's stepping down. Let's go as originally planned\n…But don't get over-confidence. You're… not good enough",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.6000000636,
      "endTime": 21.379999605800002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 16.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_05-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "……はい。うちのこと、諦めないでくれて\n本当にありがとうございます、蟻田さん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Yes. Thank you so much‚ Arita-san\nfor not giving up on me",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.5666663487,
      "endTime": 29.115895303,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 29.2999996821
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_05-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "優、見違えたわ。とても……頑張ったのね\n蟻田さんはあんな風に言っていたけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yu‚ you've changed so much. You worked so hard\nArita-san said that…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.2999996821,
      "endTime": 37.6844896952,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 37.8666676203
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_05-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "分かっとる。舞台が終わるまで、うちが油断しないよう\nあえて厳しく接してくれとる。そんな気がするわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I know. Until the end of the stage‚ he deliberately treats me strictly\nso I don't let my guard down. That's how I feel",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.8666676203,
      "endTime": 46.467960039800005,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 46.6666676203
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_05-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "それにな、うちがまだまだ下手なんは、誰より\n自分が分かっとる。だからもっとお稽古頑張ります",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Besides‚ I know better than anyone that I'm still not good enough\nThat's why I'll practice even harder",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.6666676203,
      "endTime": 54.6687764803,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 54.8666676203
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_05-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "うえぇ～ん、優ちゃ～ん、良かったよ～！！\nこれで三人一緒に舞台に出られるねぇ～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fuwaa~‚ Yu-chan‚ that was great~!!\nNow the three of us can perform on stage together!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.8666676203,
      "endTime": 63.5491396586,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 63.7333342869
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_05-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "これも、二人のアドバイスのおかげや。それに……\nうちのこと信じて待ってくれてて、ありがとな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And it's all thanks to your advice‚ both of you. And…\nthank you for believing in me and waiting for me",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.7333342869,
      "endTime": 71.9631982167,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 72.1666676203
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_05-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "……えぇ。優は必ず上達して帰って来ると信じてた\nだから私達は、私達がすべきことをして、待ってた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Yeah. I believed that Yu would definitely improve and come back\nSo‚ we did what we had to do‚ and waited",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.1666676203,
      "endTime": 81.42249533329999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 81.6333342869
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_05-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "優ちゃんだけがうまくなってもダメだもんね\n私達だってお稽古、すっごく頑張ったんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It wouldn't be enough if only Yu-chan got better\nWe practiced really hard‚ too",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.6333342869,
      "endTime": 88.01666777909999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 88.2333342869
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_05-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "そうやな。近くで支え合うだけやなくて\n離れていても信じ合える――それがうちらの関係や",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right. Not just supporting each other when we're close‚\nbut trusting each other even when we're apart—that's what our relationship is",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.2333342869,
      "endTime": 97.5048308689,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 97.7000009536
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_05-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "さぁ、舞台の幕明けまであと少し――\n気張っていこうな、二人とも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now‚ there's only a little time left until the curtain rises on the play\nLet's get pumped‚ both of you",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.7000009536,
      "endTime": 103.9389576911,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "演出家",
      "speakerNameEn": "Director",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_05-enshutu003.m4a",
      "text": "お取込み中悪いわね。舞台の衣装が届いたの\nすぐ衣装を合わせなさい。もたもたしない！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry for the inconvenience. The stage costumes have arrived\nLet's check the costume right away. Don't hesitate!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.1333342869,
      "endTime": 111.4399971326,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8733.336385200004
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 112.633330218
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_05-yu008.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……凄い……プカミちゃんになれるなんて……\nここの装飾とか原作の再現度、エグいて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow… amazing… to be Pukami-chan…\nThe decorations here and the reproduction of the original are also excellent…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.6666706721,
      "endTime": 123.15460745499999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 115.0482635442
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 117.442700386
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 123.3666706721
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_05-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "……この衣装、少し派手じゃない？　アニメでは気に\nならなかったけど……自分が着ると、恥ずかしいわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Isn't this costume a little fancy? I didn't mind it\nin the anime… I feel embarrassed when I wear it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.3666706721,
      "endTime": 132.6908426921,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 132.8333353042
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_05-yu009.m4a",
      "text": "はぁっ！　……なんちゅうことや。二人とも、リアル\n『ぷりてぃー★エンジェル』やん！　思ってた以上や！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haa! …What are you talking about. Both of you‚ real\n\"Pretty★Angel\"! It's even better than I expected!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.8333353042,
      "endTime": 140.6994125366,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 140.9000019709
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_05-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "あの……優ちゃん？　呼吸、荒いけど大丈夫？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey… Yu-chan? Your breathing is rough‚ are you okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.9000019709,
      "endTime": 146.4857843081,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 146.7000019709
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_05-yu010.m4a",
      "text": "うちのことは気にせんと、二人ともポーズ取って！\nアニメ12話の、あの感動のシーンを再現しようや？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don't worry about me‚ you two strike a pose!\nShall we recreate that touching scene from episode 12 of the anime?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.7000019709,
      "endTime": 154.8178706804,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 155.0333353042
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "演出家",
      "speakerNameEn": "Director",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_05-enshutu004.m4a",
      "text": "着替えたら早く稽古場に来なさい！　まったく……\n私語はやめなさいって何度も言ってるでしょ！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Get changed and come to the rehearsal hall quickly! Seriously…\nHow many times have I told you to don't small talk!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.0333353042,
      "endTime": 162.93335380550002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_05-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（……という、優にまつわる騒ぎは）\n（俺の知らないところで、見事に収まっていた）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（…The whole commotion surrounding Yu）\n（It was resolved wonderfully‚ from somewhere I don't know）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 163.1333536148,
      "endTime": 169.43335361479998,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 7733.334350599989
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 166.233346494
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 170.6166879654
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
