      "text": "ごめん、二人の反応がええから調子に乗ってしまって\n冗談やて。お酒なんて、一滴も飲んでへん。演技やで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry‚ I got carried away by their good reactions\nI was joking. I didn't drink a drop of alcohol. I was acting.",
